I"ª<p><b>Platform:</b> Desktop <br />
<b>Devices:</b> Oculus Rift, Logitech force 3D Joystick, Phidgets sensors. <br />
<b>Game Engine:</b> Unity.<br />
<b>Context:</b> VR-based Education/Training.<br /></p>

<p>It aims to measure the learning of users by comparing the completion of tasks with Passive Haptics and traditional controls.</p>

